parameter.name: message
parameter.subParameter:
Welcome to Devn's Auto-Queuer!
To start this tool follow these steps: 1) Open League of Legends. 2) Log into League of Legends. 3) Go to home page of League of Legends. 4) Press "OK"!
Notes: - This tool will AUTOMATICALLY start another ranked queue after you finish a game. - To stop this tool go down to your toolbar and close the program called "Actionaz" and stop searching for a game.
